latestIgtvVideos.title: Full Face using a SINGLE POWDERPUFF 🤯
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ever since Tati launched her blendiful, I've been eyeing it. But bohot hi zyada mehenga hone ke kaaran, I thought why not try using something similar, so I tried the powder puff which I had at home. 

My verdict - BROOOO.  KYA CHEEZ HAI POWDER PUFF. 
🎯It blends like a dream. And for some reason your pores look significantly smaller than usual. 
🎯It picks up every ounce of excess products making your base look flawless. 
🎯Only con? It soaks a lot of product, which in turn makes you use more product to get the result.
🎯Best way to use it? Use it as a finisher after you're done blending w a brush to get a flawless, airbrushes effect, that way you don't waste a lot of product. #igtv #makeup #makeuptutorial #makeuphacks #powderpuff #tati #fullface #wakeupandmakeup #blazin_beauties #undiscovered_muas #undiscoveredmuas #underratedmuas
